title: You Will Never Know: Tootie's May 2015 Mix
description:
Spring is in the air and Tootie's May 2015 Mix is here. The main highlight of the mix is a short set of Deep House, inspired by Ahmet Kilic's Deep House Summer Mix 2. Another inclusion worth mentioning is the otherwise unreleased Tootie-enhanced version of "Casper Slide Part 2".

  Cameo - Word Up!
  DJ Casper - Casper Slide Part 2
  Nelly - #1
  Eminem - The Way I Am
  Cosmic Gate - Somewhere Over the Rainbow
  Imany - You Will Never Know (Ivan Spell & Daniel Magre Reboot)*
  Ludwix - My Pain
  Nick Kech featuring Madilyn Bailey - The Moment*
  Lady Gaga featuring R. Kelly - Do What U Want
  Donna Summer - She Works Hard For the Money
  Gangstagrass featuring T.O.N.E-z - Long Hard Times to Come
  Imagine Dragons - Radioactive
  Soul Coughing - Super Bon Bon
  Robert Palmer - Simply Irresistible
  3 Doors Down - Life of My Own
  Nirvana - Rape Me
  Saliva - Musta Been Wrong
  Metallica - Wherever I May Roam
  Tool - Sober
  Brian McKnight - Anytime
  Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles - Count on Us
  Steel Panther - Cleveland Roxx

*Track is sourced from a MP3

All tracks are sourced from lossless material unless noted. All of the compilations' songs utilize playback gain values from Tootie's personal volume-leveling procedure, resulting in a consistent overall listening experience without the need to adjust the volume between songs. The method focuses on vocal volume.
